287
00:25:58,545 --> 00:26:00,458
Aku ingin bermain di air.

288
00:26:02,634 --> 00:26:06,153
Bersama kamu dan Sun.

289
00:26:10,854 --> 00:26:12,107
Hey kamu lagi ngapain?

290
00:26:12,107 --> 00:26:14,651
- Mengajakmu bermain di air!
- Tenaga surya!

291
00:26:22,917 --> 00:26:24,467
Apa yang sebenarnya kamu lakukan?

292
00:26:24,467 --> 00:26:26,520
Tenaga surya!

293
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:28,740
Aku membawamu ke dalam air untuk bermain.

294
00:26:29,433 --> 00:26:32,068
Nah? Sudah puas sekarang?

295
00:26:32,068 --> 00:26:33,868
Sangat.

296
00:26:36,093 --> 00:26:38,283
Kamu bilang kamu ingin bermain
dengan Little Sun, kan?

297
00:26:39,379 --> 00:26:41,033
Cobalah meniru saya.

298
00:26:41,982 --> 00:26:43,182
Meniru Anda?

299
00:26:43,182 --> 00:26:44,633
Ya.

300
00:26:44,633 --> 00:26:46,480
Cobalah menutup mata Anda.

301
00:26:47,730 --> 00:26:48,760
Ayo, pejamkan matamu.

302
00:26:48,760 --> 00:26:50,316
Oke.

303
00:26:50,316 --> 00:26:52,649
Apakah Anda ingat saat pertama kali kita tiba?

304
00:26:52,649 --> 00:26:53,772
Ya.

305
00:26:53,772 --> 00:26:56,091
Apa yang tadi kamu katakan ingin kamu lakukan?

306
00:26:56,091 --> 00:26:58,251
Cobalah membayangkannya.

307
00:27:14,749 --> 00:27:16,348
Hai!

308
00:27:43,751 --> 00:27:49,114
Little Sun,
meskipun kita belum pernah bertemu secara langsung,

309
00:27:49,114 --> 00:27:54,161
Aku selalu tahu dan merasakan kehadiranmu
